    <div class="main review-item" id="6463914">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6463914/" class="title-link">关于此书的一个总结</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6463914"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2704484/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2704484-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2704484/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">船山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-16 19:24:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6463914_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书从名字上来看就可以知道，是针对亚里士多德的《工具论》而来的，培根认为亚里士多德用逻辑的范畴来规范客观世界，使自然屈从于逻辑学，所以亚里士多德的逻辑学在培根看来不是一种有价值的工具，因此培根认为有必要重新创立一种新的所谓工具来代替之。《新工具》就是培根...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6463914/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6463914_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6463914_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5664043">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5664043/" class="title-link">Francis Bacon《新工具（Novum Organum）》小摘要</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5664043"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47643947-54.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">江绪林</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-22"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-22 18:31:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5664043_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  【按语：在书名上，Bacon（1561-1625）的《新工具（Novum Organum）》（1620）有意针对着亚里士多德的《工具论》：因为亚里士多德的《工具论》不仅包括三段论逻辑的讨论，而且也包含着像《范畴篇》等形而上学的内容，因而Bacon试图提供一种不同的、注重经验和实验的思想路径。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5664043/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5664043_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5664043_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



