  <ul class="bs more-after">
      
      <li style="border: none">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bplisn.net.cn%2FBookSearch.aspx%3FISBN%3D7-100-02383-1&amp;subject=7100023831&amp;type=borrow&amp;library=10007&amp;link2key=5e18a0d1f6" target="_blank">北京市公共图书馆(1)</a>
